    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/4f360ef986d390006e3a0768bb3cb432.poster.avif?t=1768558968\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/4f360ef986d390006e3a0768bb3cb432.webm?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/4f360ef986d390006e3a0768bb3cb432.mp4?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款 roguelike 骰组构建游戏中，远古恐惧对你穷追不舍。你需要打造强力连招，对抗协同作战的敌人，重新扔出技能以求生存。不断升级武器，打造致命的连携效应，最终碾压强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/0c8ec4a907b1a686d011acaf51d3a35a.poster.avif?t=1768558968\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/0c8ec4a907b1a686d011acaf51d3a35a.webm?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/0c8ec4a907b1a686d011acaf51d3a35a.mp4?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >连携机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人的连携机制：</strong>敌人会根据战斗中其他人的情况，获得新的能力和互动方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家与敌人的连携机制：</strong>玩家可与某些敌人进行互动，获得改善战斗体验的增益。比如说，杀害某种特殊敌人能对它身边的其他人造成伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>元素的连携机制：</strong>元素伤害也可造成连携。例如，寒冷能减轻流血伤害，疾病可以蔓延至陷入寒冷或是流血状态的单位。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/9c5de69569f7ae83be448d7cc0099f70.poster.avif?t=1768558968\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/9c5de69569f7ae83be448d7cc0099f70.webm?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/9c5de69569f7ae83be448d7cc0099f70.mp4?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有深度的战斗</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复杂的首领机制：</strong>比方说，会遇到小型首领突袭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你在前进，敌人也在变强：</strong>关卡越深入，你所遭遇的敌人也会越加强大，更会获得全新的能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动：</strong>和环境进行互动，探索新的玩法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>移动机制：</strong>你操控的角色并不局限在一处，可抓准时机躲避特定攻击，并且大多数物品都有位置要求。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/1d5a49dc8a7090471de4554f812cfcfd.poster.avif?t=1768558968\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/1d5a49dc8a7090471de4554f812cfcfd.webm?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/1d5a49dc8a7090471de4554f812cfcfd.mp4?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >远古恐惧</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管控好你的气味：</strong>在大地图上前进须步步为营。黑暗就在你的身后。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动用理智：</strong>癫狂是把双刃剑。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/2bbb3a7b5b4c0a0655a2a994df7c0035.poster.avif?t=1768558968\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/2bbb3a7b5b4c0a0655a2a994df7c0035.webm?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227330/extras/2bbb3a7b5b4c0a0655a2a994df7c0035.mp4?t=1768558968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >碾压强敌！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品连携：</strong>用强力物品构建骰组，将其连携效果发挥到极致。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以你的方式升级物品：</strong>根据你的玩法和骰组，以任意方式升级物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重新掷骰：</strong>骰子只是灵活的卡牌。牺牲理智值重新掷骰，扔出合适的能力。</p></li></ul>",
